# OTFlow Schedule Paper Plan

This is the canonical experiment plan for the deployed `TVD-Scheduler` workspace on `yzn3090`.

## Thesis

The paper studies fixed-grid inference schedules under a shared `OTFlow` backbone and asks how scheduler choice changes performance at matched realized NFE.

The main contribution is the **scheduler**. The backbone sweep is an OTFlow-only budget study used to ensure all fixed-model checkpoints are prepared for fair schedule comparisons, not a multi-backbone comparison track.

